["Boulazac (Limousin: Bolasac) is a former commune in the Dordogne department in southwestern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Boulazac-Isle-Manoire.[2]","The Boulazac Basket Dordogne (BBD) is a French basketball club, based in Boulazac.","This Dordogne geographical article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]